Getperl downloads, configures, builds and tests perl.
Project home page: http://github.com/rsp/getperl

Usage: getperl VERSION
       getperl VERSION PREFIX

Downloads: http://www.cpan.org/src/5.0/perl-VERSION.tar.gz
and builds for installation in PREFIX or /opt/perl by default.
If PREFIX is 'v' or 'V' it is equivalent to /opt/perl-VERSION

Examples: getperl 5.12.2
          getperl 5.12.2 v
          getperl 5.12.2 /usr/local

